
Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And	I go to Page 04 of Elbow MRI

When I select 'Finding' radio button
Then 'Finding' dropdown menu is enabled

When I select 'Arthrosis' from the dropdown menu
Then 'Add new finding' button is enabled
And 'Osteophytes' checkbox is enabled
And 'Subchondral sclerosis' checkbox is enabled
And 'Joint space narrowing' checkbox is enabled
And 'Loose body' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Loose body' checkbox
Then 'Max. diameter' input field is enabled
And '> 1 loose body' checkbox is enabled

When I select '> 1 loose body' checkbox
Then '> 1 loose body' dropdown menu is enabled
